{% block body %}<h2 id="typeface">Typeface</h2>
<p>TCDS uses the <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto">Roboto</a> specimen from <a href="https://fonts.google.com/">Google Fonts</a>.</p>
<h2 id="type-scale">Type scale</h2>
<p>TCDS uses a modular type scale based on a baseline text size of 1 rem (= 16 pixels) and a ratio of 1.25. The resulting sizes larger than the baseline are calculated as <span class="font-slab">1 rem &times; 1.25<sup>n</sup></span> where <span class="font-slab">n = 1..4</span>.</p>
